<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a49c4dd-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s4910"><num value="4910">§ 4910.</num><heading> Nonduplication</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall ensure that information systems created or developed pursuant to this chapter do not unnecessarily duplicate information systems available from other Federal agencies or from the private sector.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a49c4de-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/418/tV/s5410">Pub. L. 100–418, title V, § 5410</ref>, <date date="1988-08-23">Aug. 23, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/1467">102 Stat. 1467</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
